SS |\n   121→| AC4 | PASS |\n   122→| AC5 | PASS |\n   123→| AC6 | PASS |\n   124→| AC7 | PASS |\n   125→\n   126→**Final Result: ALL_PASS (7/7 ACs)**\n   127→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01M5ggaWpBnpHGzCP9ij59UW","session_id":"c452ddd6-f9a0-4cb1-9871-4264c6441698","uuid":"906c2e41-c372-4618-addb-faf79ac082cc","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:30:35.798Z"}
