able, runtime-provable] (AC3)\n    59→ Test Files  1 passed (1)\n    60→ Tests  1 passed (1)\n    61→```\n    62→<!-- /showboat exec -->\n    63→\n    64→---\n    65→\n    66→## AC 4: maxTier(['test-provable']) returns 'test-provable'\n    67→\n    68→**Verdict:** PASS\n    69→\n    70→<!-- showboat exec: verify maxTier AC4 test -->\n    71→```bash\n    72→npx vitest run src/modules/verify/__tests__/verification-tier.test.ts -t \"AC4\" 2>&1 | grep -E \"PASS|FAIL|✓|✗\"\n    73→```\n    74→\n    75→```output\n    76→ ✓ maxTier > returns test-provable for single test-provable (AC4)\n    77→ Test Files  1 passed (1)\n    78→ Tests  1 passed (1)\n    79→```\n    80→<!-- /showboat exec -->"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01M5ggaWpBnpHGzCP9ij59UW","session_id":"c452ddd6-f9a0-4cb1-9871-4264c6441698","uuid":"e5379c4c-6670-41fc-a3b1-1cc3d37f980e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:30:57.601Z"}
